OL,3,CGreens leader Zack Polanski admits he
OL,4,Cdid not vote in local elections
OL,6,FGreen Party Leader Zack Polanski has
OL,7,Fadmitted he did not vote in last
OL,8,Fweek's local elections as he "fell
OL,9,Fshort of time" to register while
OL,10,Fmoving house.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for the Greens
OL,13,Fpreviously told The Times Polanski may
OL,14,Fhave used a postal vote, but the party
OL,15,Fhas since confirmed this was a
OL,16,F"miscommunication".
OL,18,FIn a video posted earlier this month,
OL,19,FPolanski told Hackney's mayoral
OL,20,Fcandidate, Zoe Garbett, "you have my
OL,21,Fvote".
OL,26,@|D@Nxr
