OL,3,CGreens leader Zack Polanski admits he
OL,4,Cdid not vote in local elections
OL,6,FBut in a statement to the Independent,
OL,7,Fthe party said: "Zack was unable to
OL,8,Fvote. He was in the process of moving,
OL,9,Fand when that fell through, he moved
OL,10,Fin as a lodger in rented accommodation.
OL,12,F"He fell short of time to register at
OL,13,Fnew place, especially given the extra
OL,14,Fprocess he would need to go through to
OL,15,Fregister anonymously.
OL,17,F"Zack has recently had increased
OL,18,Fsecurity concerns after being the
OL,19,Ftarget of antisemitic and homophobic
OL,20,Fabuse."
OL,26,@oD@QOUyD@AOU|D@GO]
