OL,3,CGreens leader Zack Polanski admits he
OL,4,Cdid not vote in local elections
OL,6,FPolanski has overseen a surge in
OL,7,Fsupport for the Greens since he took
OL,8,Fover as leader last year, but has
OL,9,Frecently come under increased scrutiny
OL,10,Fover past statements.
OL,12,FEarlier this week, the Greens leader
OL,13,Fadmitted he may have failed to pay the
OL,14,Fcorrect council tax while living on a
OL,15,Fhouseboat in east London.
OL,17,FIt was an "unintentional mistake", and
OL,18,FPolanski had "immediately taken steps"
OL,19,Fto pay any tax owed, a party
OL,20,Fspokesperson said.
OL,26,@zD@fO]
