OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778839648
OL,3,CGreens leader Zack Polanski admits he
OL,4,Cdid not vote in local elections
OL,6,FThey said he only stayed on the boat
OL,7,F"occasionally", but then issued an
OL,8,Fapology from the leader late on Monday
OL,9,Fnight.
OL,11,FIt followed The Times reporting seeing
OL,12,Fan advertisement for the sale of the
OL,13,Fboat in which Polanski's partner
OL,14,Fwrote: "We are moving to a house and
OL,15,Fso will sadly be leaving the gorgeous
OL,16,Fcommunity behind."
OL,18,FThe Green Party previously told the
OL,19,Fnewspaper that Polanski rented a room
OL,20,Fat another address where council tax
OL,21,Fwas included in the rent.
OL,26,@vD@HOUxD@RO]
