OL,3,CGreens leader Zack Polanski admits he
OL,4,Cdid not vote in local elections
OL,6,FPolanski has faced a series of
OL,7,Fcontroversies around the local
OL,8,Felections.
OL,10,FEarlier this month, he acknowledged he
OL,11,Fwas wrong to say he was a spokesman
OL,12,Ffor the British Red Cross, a claim
OL,13,Fwhich he made as he campaigned to
OL,14,Fbecome the party's deputy leader back
OL,15,Fin 2022.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
