OL,3,CGreens leader Zack Polanski admits he
OL,4,Cdid not vote in local elections
OL,6,FLast week, he admitted his mistake,
OL,7,Ftelling the BBC he had hosted
OL,8,Ffundraisers for the charity, adding:
OL,9,F"I used the wrong word, and I accept
OL,10,Fthat, but I would essentially take
OL,11,Fwords on stage with me and speak."
OL,13,FITV News has approached the Green
OL,14,FParty for comment.
